{"tid":2225824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭班主是特朗普團隊背後金主, 最強支持者","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:21:12.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"981e82a9c0829cdbb3afd1bf25ea2ed49bcda981","tid":2225824,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"Elliott創辦人 屬美國共和黨金主<br />\n<br />\nSinger最初是「反特朗普」陣營，並批評其提議的經濟政策會引致全球大衰退。不過特朗普去年2月一個記者會上，提及Singer到訪白宮交流經濟政策意見，「佢曾經Anti-Trump、Never Trump，係一個好強烈嘅反對者，但依家就係我強大嘅盟友。」《CNBC》引述消息指Singer曾於2016年贊助特朗普參選美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/republican-mega-donor-and-converted-trump-supporter-paul-singer-buys-stake-in-twitter-and-plans-to-oust-jack-dorsey/ar-BB10A5uV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Frepublican-mega-donor-and-converted-trump-supporter-paul-singer-buys-stake-in-twitter-and-plans-to-oust-jack-dorsey%2Far-BB10A5uV&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1xZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=fee1ed25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/politics/republican-mega-donor-and-converted-trump-supporter-paul-singer-buys-stake-in-twitter-and-plans-to-oust-jack-dorsey/ar-BB10A5uV</a>"},{"pid":"1aaf32c9a82ac23a6f9a346a3e4f11febdb924b7","tid":2225824,"uid":361041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b546271c1138493df0f9d8f9d70edb71d1d81079","tid":2225824,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"米國佬不嬲唔識波<br />\n米蘭今次中伏=.="}]}